jsoul.midi

Class Instrument

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsoul.midi.Instrument

  • public class Instrument
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a MIDI instrument. Contains static fields for 128 different MIDI instruments. Useful for building Tracks.
    Author:
    Andrew Goldin
